           EVALUATE    WRK-PARA-YKZKBN
      *        全体
               WHEN    0
                   IF      TNS-YKZKBN      =   3
                       CONTINUE
                   ELSE
                       MOVE    1               TO  FLG-OK
                   END-IF
      *        内服薬
               WHEN    1
                   IF      TNS-YKZKBN      =   1
                       MOVE    1               TO  FLG-OK
                   END-IF
      *        注射薬
               WHEN    2
                   IF      TNS-YKZKBN      =   4
                       MOVE    1               TO  FLG-OK
                   END-IF
      *        外用薬
               WHEN    3
      *****(00.00.01)******UPD-START************
                   IF      TNS-YKZKBN      =   6
                       MOVE    1               TO  FLG-OK
                   END-IF
      *****(00.00.01)******UPD-END**************
