                   UNTIL ( IDX         >   7 )
                   OR    ( IDZ         =   CNT-MAX )
               COMPUTE IDZ                 =   IDZ +   1
      *        科名編集
               MOVE    WRK-TAI-NAIYO(IDZ)
                                           TO  HCMG001-TAI-NAIYO(IDX)
               IF      (IDZ            =   CNT-MAX )
                   MOVE    "合計"          TO  HCMG001-TAI-NAIYO(IDX)
