      *****************************************************************
      *   帳票Ｚ編集処理
      *****************************************************************
       400-ZHEN-SURYO-SET-SEC      SECTION.
      *
      *    数量Ｚ編集
           MOVE    SPACE           TO  WRK-SURYO-X
           MOVE    WRK-SURYO-S1    TO  WRK-SURYO-Z1
      *
      *    数量小数点以下編集
           MOVE    ZERO            TO  FLG-SP
           PERFORM VARYING CNT-KETA    FROM    3   BY  -1
                   UNTIL ( CNT-KETA    <   1 )
