      *    点数Ｚ編集
           MOVE    SPACE           TO  WRK-TEN-X
           MOVE    WRK-TEN-S1      TO  WRK-TEN-Z1
      *
      *    点数小数点以下編集
           MOVE    ZERO            TO  FLG-SP
           PERFORM VARYING CNT-KETA    FROM    2   BY  -1
                   UNTIL ( CNT-KETA    <   1 )
               IF        ( WRK-TEN-S2(CNT-KETA:1) NOT =   ZERO )
